"Grylli pẹlu awọn itọnisọna ti a ṣe sinu ni gbogbo ohun elo lati ṣe iranlọwọ "
"fun ọ ṣe atunto ati ṣakoso iṣeto rẹ."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Oju ewe yii pese akopọ ti awọn ẹya pataki ati awọn ọna asopọ taara si ibiti "
"wọn ti le ṣakoso."

